2025-11-07  Andres26  andrescamorao9@gmail.com
    2025-11-7 Main changes
    
    * Moved 'CPU.S' to 'include/arch/x86/asm/'
    * The code of 'enter_realmode' and 'enter_protmode' moved to function instead
      of macro
    
      enter_realmode -> call to 'switch_to_real_mode' routine
      enter_protmode -> call to 'switch_to_prot_mode' routine
    
    * Makefile:
      - Added 'fs/vfs.c'
      - Added 'fs/fat.c'
    * Moved all asm routines to 'blib.S' (bootlib)
      - Deleted 'port.S'
      - Deleted 'intX_handler.S'
      - Deleted 'memory.S'
      - Suport for INT15,E280
    * 'loader.S'
      - 'switch_to_X_mode' routine
      - Changed GDT macros
    * 'fat.c'
      - Rewrite all driver
      - Support for detect, mount, unmount and open function
      - Moved file manager to 'vfs.c'
      - 'path' and 'subdir' names find with tokens (via strtok)
      - struct fat_fs (internal fs info)
      - struct fat_internal_file -> deleted some entries and added struct file f
      - Suport for subdirs
    * 'vfs.c'
      - Support for file descriptor
      - Support for detect, mount, unmount and open function
      - '*_register_fs'
        - Register FS info in 'special' table
        - For register FS, find in each entry until finding an empty entry
        - TODO: improve this
      - '*_detect'
        - Detect FS from disk
      - '*_mount'
        - Register disk descriptor in table
        - For detect FS is the same process as 'vfs_register_fs'
      - '*_unmount'
        - Delete FS descriptor from array
      - '*_open'
        - File handler from FAT12 old driver
    
        This is the path format '/mount_ident/path/to/file.txt'
        mount identifier valid values: 'A - Z' (not case-sensitive)
    
      - '*_close'
        - Delete file descriptor from file array
    - 'mm.c'
      - struct memory info
      - Get memory info with 'memory_init'
    - 'video.c'
      - Improved VGA driver
    - 'CHB_UTIL' compiler definition for enable internal FS structs in 'fat.h'
    - 'fatinfo.c' and 'mkbs12.c' deleted internal fat structs from '.c' file
    - 'util/Makefile' added 'CHB_UTIL' compiler definition
    
    Signed-off-by: Andres26 <andrescamorao9@gmail.com>
    

